<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_02_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->

    <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema511_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_02_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">분수만큼 색칠하고, 알맞은 말에 ○표 하세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box dir_col gap_20">
          <div class="flex dir_col gap_20 top">
            <div class="flex align_center gap_60">
              <div class="fraction_box fraction1">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>5</span>
              </div>
              <div class="">
                <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="3">
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="num_area">
                  <span class="txt0">0</span>
                  <span class="txt1">1</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center gap_60">
              <div class="fraction_box fraction2">
                <span>6</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="">
                <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="6">
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                  <button type="button"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="num_area">
                  <span class="txt0">0</span>
                  <span class="txt1">1</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bottom">
            <div class="flex align_center justify_center fraction_text">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>5</span>
              </div>
              과
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>6</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
              은 크기가 (
              <div class="boolean_wrap">
                <button class="button1" data-answer-single="true"><span lang="y">같은</span></button>,
                <button class="button2" data-answer-single="false"><span lang="y">다른</span></button>
              </div>
              ) 분수입니다.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </div>
                은 전체를 똑같이 5로 나눈 것 중의 3만큼 색칠하고,&nbsp;
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>6</span>
                  <span>10</span>
                </div>
                은 전체를 똑같이 10으로 나눈 것 중의 6만큼 색칠합니다. 색칠한 부분의 크기가 같으므로&nbsp;
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </div>
                과&nbsp;
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>6</span>
                  <span>10</span>
                </div>
                은 크기가 같은 분수입니다.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
